OL,3,CGordon Lyons breached ministerial code
OL,4,Cover social media comments, report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FGordon Lyons has been found to have
OL,8,Fbreached the ministerial code of
OL,9,Fconduct over social media comments
OL,10,Fmade during riots in June last year.
OL,12,FAn independent investigation said the
OL,13,Fcommunities minister's actions fell
OL,14,Fshort of standards on leadership,
OL,15,Faccountability and community relations.
OL,17,FThe findings relate to posts about the
OL,18,Frelocation of families to Larne
OL,19,FLeisure Centre following unrest in
OL,20,FBallymena.
